Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.16,0:21:36.43,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}I love you  I trust you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.53,0:21:41.83,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}多麼想分擔你的孤寂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.96,0:21:47.13,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}I love you  I trust you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.31,0:21:52.70,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}無論身處黑暗或是光明
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.76,0:21:59.79,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}只要在一起就可以相信
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.92,0:22:05.21,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}永遠不再分離
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----Dialogue
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.60,0:00:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就沒有別的辦法了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.14,0:00:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.67,0:00:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候…她…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.71,0:00:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不是艾紐·裡特納了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.15,0:00:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼說得這麼肯定?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.48,0:00:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.49,0:00:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 我可以確定的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.45,0:00:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不那麼做的話 萊爾·狄蘭迪就會死
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.75,0:00:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.63,0:00:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易絲·哈勒維也是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.64,0:00:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她被什麼東西占據了而不能自拔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.25,0:00:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.17,0:00:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最近有些地方不對勁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.03,0:00:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和一直以來不同
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.35,0:00:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了檢查艦內系統 將暫時切斷電源
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.41,0:01:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,檢查完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.74,0:01:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恢復一般供電
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.95,0:01:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船控系統 恢復
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.76,0:01:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切正常
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.35,0:01:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米蕾娜 敵艦如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.63,0:01:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子已經不在可視范圍內了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.91,0:01:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要放松
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.69,0:01:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許會像之前一樣中陰招	
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.60,0:01:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提艾利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.50,0:01:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯米拉琪小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.73,0:01:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在系統當機時 好像接到了緊急暗號通信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.44,0:01:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內容是?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.72,0:01:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只寫了宙域坐標
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.71,0:01:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地點是拉格朗日5
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.75,0:01:40.36,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}拉格朗日5 Eclipse
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.39,0:01:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,建設中斷的殖民地 Eclipse
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.57,0:01:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.18,0:01:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.83,0:01:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還不能…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.31,0:03:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去拉格朗日5?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.77,0:03:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要回應那個發送坐標的人嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.39,0:03:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很在意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.75,0:03:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 剎那也堅持要去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.43,0:03:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那他?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.79,0:03:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也贊成
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.97,0:03:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊恩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.35,0:03:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉格朗日5那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.72,0:03:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,避難的琳達他們也在繼續著研究
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.91,0:03:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順利的話 也可以拿到計劃中的新裝備
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.59,0:03:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到達那裡的話 還能進行Gundam的維修
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.12,0:04:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.78,0:04:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我來掌舵?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.99,0:04:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉塞受傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.32,0:04:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須找人來保護托勒密
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.55,0:04:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算不讓我上戰場嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.60,0:04:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和斯米盧諾夫大佐這麼約定的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.34,0:04:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 聽我一次吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.11,0:04:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不聽!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.06,0:04:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索瑪·皮瑞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.83,0:04:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的戰斗持續下去的話 總有一天你…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.35,0:04:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密會迂回前進 引開敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.35,0:04:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁這個機會 去和通信者接觸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.88,0:04:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.60,0:04:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.61,0:04:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是去幫助人吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.98,0:04:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的話 我會協助的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.14,0:04:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊爾…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.08,0:04:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前的事 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.41,0:05:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過於感情用事了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.37,0:05:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不配做機師
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.88,0:05:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊爾 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.85,0:05:05.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.67,0:05:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會戰斗的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.94,0:05:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.38,0:05:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.39,0:05:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滅了那幫變革者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.13,0:05:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是為了KATARON 也不是為了天行者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.93,0:05:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要以我自己的意志和他們戰斗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.25,0:05:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.91,0:05:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.74,0:06:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密第一第三艙門打開
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.72,0:06:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發射時機交予00
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.83,0:06:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.99,0:06:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,00 剎那·F·塞艾 出發
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.85,0:06:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0 Raiser 沙慈·庫洛斯洛特 出發
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.95,0:06:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0 Raiser DOCKING-MODE
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.61,0:06:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,00 Raiser 飛往拉格朗日5
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.76,0:06:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光學攝像機捕捉到天行者的宇宙船
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.45,0:06:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路線變更了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.20,0:06:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續追擊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.67,0:06:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.39,0:06:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}第三艦隊 航向改變
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.20,0:06:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擊敗天行者的話 反對勢力的氣勢也會下降
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.27,0:06:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不能再信任那些自我主義的家伙了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.45,0:06:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了回應片桐司令的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.13,0:06:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要用壓倒性的戰力殲滅他們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.53,0:07:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.33,0:07:02.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連艾紐也被打敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.19,0:07:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可是變革者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.25,0:07:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,00 Gundam…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.48,0:07:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿下你了 00
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.83,0:07:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.05,0:07:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.07,0:07:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種戰斗方式… 不僅僅是依靠MS的性能…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.97,0:07:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,00的駕駛員開始革新了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.26,0:07:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈? 你在說什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.51,0:07:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣話解釋不了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.83,0:07:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想說他是純種
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.70,0:07:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那·F·塞艾…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.16,0:08:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他會成為人類最初的變革者嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.55,0:08:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.63,0:08:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在這裡啊 准尉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.25,0:08:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新型MA的維修…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.91,0:08:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.92,0:08:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.74,0:08:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准尉 怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.35,0:08:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說了別…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.43,0:08:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾你們了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.52,0:08:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr.武士道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.81,0:08:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.25,0:08:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和准尉的特別命令下達了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.84,0:08:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准備出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.37,0:08:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.37,0:08:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓我同行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.46,0:08:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會去征得古德曼准將的同意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.48,0:08:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.50,0:08:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得能跟上我和准尉的機體嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.32,0:08:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距到達目標還要花幾天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.57,0:08:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.28,0:08:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就按你說的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.32,0:09:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最近有些地方不對勁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.00,0:09:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那 你要改變 代替不能改變的我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.40,0:09:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.28,0:09:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 變了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.73,0:09:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那終點有著什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.95,0:09:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩琳嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.97,0:09:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞斯 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.93,0:09:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擦傷而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.55,0:09:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也沒事真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.19,0:09:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到宇宙去?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.89,0:09:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和聯邦軍政變派殘黨接觸了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.73,0:09:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在支部幾乎全滅 再留在地上太危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.94,0:09:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 宇宙中KATARON的戰力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.78,0:09:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會悲觀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.50,0:10:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在 有些人正在用與我們
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.14,0:10:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及天行者所不同方法行動著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.17,0:10:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這首歌是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.02,0:10:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 瑪麗娜公主的歌正在向外傳播
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.64,0:10:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗娜的歌在世界上…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.77,0:10:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.07,0:10:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想人們總是渴望和平的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.40,0:10:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗娜公主的歌描述了沒有紛爭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.51,0:10:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,共同生存的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.01,0:10:31.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許我們只是在一味地否定他人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.85,0:10:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而遺忘了相互理解的道理
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.68,0:10:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相互理解…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.33,0:10:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗娜卻一直在追求?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.26,0:10:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信這條道路的未來…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.65,0:10:58.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有人出現在指定地點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.58,0:11:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐 天行者真的會來嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.56,0:11:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.04,0:11:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 不來的話 世界就會變為變革者所有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.70,0:11:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為裡本斯·阿爾馬克的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.00,0:11:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼娜·崔尼蒂什麼時候站到變革者一邊的?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.73,0:11:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別總是向別人提問 自己思考
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.72,0:11:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為你一直這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.04,0:11:23.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才會讓我成為王家的當家的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.22,0:11:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為哥哥你沒有當家的氣質
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.13,0:11:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的人生才扭曲了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.71,0:11:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才渴望世界的變革
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.88,0:11:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是用地位、名譽和資產來交換
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.31,0:11:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我是為了修正自己的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.65,0:11:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把握自己的將來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.38,0:11:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追隨我到最後吧 紅龍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.29,0:11:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有這個責任
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.33,0:11:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼膩歪的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.21,0:11:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.85,0:12:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.98,0:12:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼娜·崔尼蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.80,0:12:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最討厭你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.99,0:12:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永別了 大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.38,0:12:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留美!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.06,0:12:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最討厭你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.22,0:12:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永別了 大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.75,0:12:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留美!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.59,0:12:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅龍…!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.21,0:12:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我讓開!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.86,0:12:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄長…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.21,0:12:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留… 留美
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.93,0:12:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.68,0:12:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄長!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.40,0:12:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡由我…!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.73,0:12:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.51,0:12:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還耍帥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.26,0:12:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束了麼 結束了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.63,0:13:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就先這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.71,0:13:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.82,0:13:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.83,0:13:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣計劃就重寫了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.22,0:13:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既不是伊奧利亞也不是裡本斯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.78,0:13:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是我自己的計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.06,0:13:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.66,0:13:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS無法到達指定坐標
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.34,0:13:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機體控制 交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.64,0:13:24.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.46,0:13:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在前面麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.80,0:13:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那·F·塞艾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.15,0:13:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王留美?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.26,0:13:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 受傷了麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.32,0:14:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有任何事情 不說了先拿著這個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.50,0:14:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.40,0:14:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維塔本體的位置記錄在上面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.96,0:14:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維塔本體麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.87,0:14:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是被變革者得知這件事的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.20,0:14:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維塔就會被轉移
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.60,0:14:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要盡快 去奪回維塔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.69,0:14:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.28,0:14:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起從這裡撤離吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.89,0:14:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒關系的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.40,0:14:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.67,0:14:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不能和你一起走的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.62,0:14:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要擔心我了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.63,0:14:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.40,0:14:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不能和你們一起走的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.21,0:14:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為追求的東西可是不同的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.52,0:14:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.03,0:14:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.82,0:14:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊… 什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.46,0:14:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那架機體是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.25,0:14:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4年不見了啊 少年
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.01,0:14:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個男的是…!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.80,0:15:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混賬…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.54,0:15:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.78,0:15:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想失去Gundam的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.68,0:15:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你能夠回應我的期望
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.73,0:15:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼期望?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.49,0:15:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認真地決一勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.46,0:15:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.46,0:15:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 古拉哈姆·艾卡 但求與你做個了解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.65,0:15:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. 武士道…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.65,0:15:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是裡本斯唆使他來的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.73,0:15:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不惜如此地想要決戰麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.33,0:15:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.49,0:15:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我的天空劃下傷痕 將我的同胞和恩師奪去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.49,0:15:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連我作為Flag Fighter
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.56,0:15:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後的尊嚴也盡數打碎的不是別人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.47,0:15:41.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是你和Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.31,0:15:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.83,0:15:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是已經超越了愛 又超越了憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.99,0:15:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為了我此生的宿命!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.74,0:15:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿命?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.61,0:15:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要笑我自作多情麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.23,0:15:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 不要忘記了最初進行武力介入的可是Gundam!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.45,0:16:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個男人也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.39,0:16:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們而歪曲了的存在…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.30,0:16:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 我就接受在此了結吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.15,0:16:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,望你能盡全力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.70,0:16:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈 把控制交回這邊來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.61,0:16:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你准備跟他打?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.79,0:16:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有其他的辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.86,0:16:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我所期望的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.80,0:16:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修羅之路!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.19,0:16:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,00 Riser!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.56,0:16:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豪傑加強版!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.75,0:16:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將目標…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.53,0:16:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 決一…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.56,0:16:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅逐!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.47,0:16:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生死!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.22,0:16:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天行者也好 變革者也好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.72,0:16:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有兄長獻上性命 完成變革
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.01,0:16:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會將那之後美好的未來…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.02,0:16:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種東西 沒可能會有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.10,0:16:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼娜 為什麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.79,0:17:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說過的吧 我最討厭的就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.47,0:17:03.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服從你只是為了活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.32,0:17:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微裝得聽話點你相信得還真快
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.48,0:17:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.08,0:17:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的使命已經結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.11,0:17:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化成灰塵了呢～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.19,0:17:27.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是你一直把人家當道具對待的懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.84,0:17:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為了活下去的話什麼都會去做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.75,0:17:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了得到幸福的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.69,0:17:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對的 服從變革者也是為了這個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.93,0:17:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為哥哥們的仇都還沒報
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.11,0:17:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時機到了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.65,0:17:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓我隆重地反咬破你們的喉嚨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.78,0:17:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話你的使命也結束了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.44,0:17:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈羅?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.35,0:17:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亂來的家伙得要接受懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.97,0:17:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變革者!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.98,0:17:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對你的制裁者會出現的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.92,0:18:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼制裁者?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.57,0:18:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.39,0:18:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是 那家伙…?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.39,0:18:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有趣 哥哥們的仇人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.75,0:18:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢 某種意義上說的確實算是仇人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.55,0:18:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 什麼!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.06,0:18:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是它
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.53,0:18:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那架Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.58,0:18:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把媽媽… 和爸爸殺掉的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.72,0:18:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候的Gundam!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.87,0:18:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.72,0:18:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那部機體 是Throne!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.34,0:18:39.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把露易絲家人殺掉的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.83,0:18:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 露易絲·哈勒維!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.62,0:18:42.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易絲?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.56,0:18:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種復仇…!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.94,0:18:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易絲!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.12,0:18:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過要全力作戰!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.36,0:18:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸的仇人? 就算是我好了!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.51,0:18:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別以為就你張狂!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.83,0:19:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被制造出來 被丟上戰場…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.19,0:19:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能死在 這種地方!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.58,0:19:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢 不想死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.06,0:19:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 媽媽和爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.58,0:19:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連這句話都沒機會說!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.81,0:19:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡~~!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.48,0:19:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把Throne給…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.71,0:19:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易絲!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.73,0:19:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不專心戰斗嗎!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.38,0:19:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. 武士道正在和Gundam決斗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.61,0:19:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准尉的機體呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.33,0:19:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.76,0:19:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.12,0:19:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.13,0:20:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我報仇了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.15,0:20:02.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打倒Gundam了哦!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.04,0:20:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准尉…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.80,0:20:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 爸爸 在哪裡?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.50,0:20:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.71,0:20:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做到了哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.23,0:20:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…所以……
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.64,0:20:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來誇獎我呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.91,0:20:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…誇我…做得好吧……
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.85,0:22:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活著的…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.57,0:22:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是為此活著的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.37,0:22:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算要成為變革者的傀儡也好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.66,0:22:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有這武士道…!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.02,0:22:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做到這個地步…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.35,0:22:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.39,0:22:34.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,專心戰斗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.78,0:22:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.97,0:22:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本了結不完
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.75,0:22:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.85,0:22:42.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.08,0:22:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.14,0:22:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.37,0:23:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於 覺醒了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.48,0:23:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡究竟是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.54,0:23:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說我已經成佛涅磐了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.09,0:23:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.44,0:23:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.56,0:23:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是 量子集中的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.90,0:23:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼夢話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.92,0:23:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.48,0:23:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奧利亞·肖漢博格制造Gundam…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.40,0:23:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 制造GN-DRIVER的理由…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.22,0:23:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.91,0:23:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武力介入只是為此的布局
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.42,0:23:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奧利亞的目的是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.24,0:23:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引導人類的革新
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.43,0:23:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.65,0:23:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在變革之中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.79,0:24:01.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為奪回維塔
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.35,0:24:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強行突破A-LAWS艦隊的任務開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.46,0:24:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.43,0:24:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了未來
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.50,0:24:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算要背負罪孽
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.94,0:24:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要這戰斗能另明日重生…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.30,0:00:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
