Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.76,0:10:30.19,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\a6\fs45}星????　明日?來?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.35,0:10:35.38,IN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\a6\fs45}????行?????
